Package it.polimi.ingsw.utils.messages.clientMessages

Interface ClientMessage

All Superinterfaces:
java.io.Serializable
All Known Subinterfaces:
ConfigurationMessage, GameControllerHandleable, TurnControllerHandleable
All Known Implementing Classes:
ActivateProductionMessage, BuyDevCardMessage, EndTurnMessage, GameModeChoiceMessage, LeaderActionMessage, LeaderChoiceMessage, MoveResourcesMessage, NumOfPlayerChoiceMessage, PositioningMessage, ResourceChoiceMessage, TakeResourcesFromMarketMessage, UsernameChoiceMessage
public interface ClientMessage
extends java.io.Serializable
Interface that provides an abstraction of messages that remote host can expect from client. It inherit from Serializable class in order to be sent through the network.
